# TQ-3: Regression Prevention
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Every code change

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Regression Check: Ensuring new changes do not break existing functionality.

ENFORCE: Regression tests must run on every code change; failures block progression.
PROHIBIT: Skipping regression checks for any reason.
ON VIOLATION: Halt skill execution → notify orchestrator and engineer.
